# Dashboard UX Patterns

## Layout

- **Top bar + tabs** â€” no sidebar. `header` â†’ `tab-nav` â†’ `main`
- Desktop: icon + text tabs. Tablet: icon-only tabs. Mobile: hamburger dropdown
- `LayoutService.isFullscreen()` hides header/tabs for fullscreen views
- Background: `bg-base-200`. Content area: `p-4 lg:p-6`

## Shared Component Library

Always compose pages with shared components instead of raw HTML:

| Component | Path | Purpose |
|-----------|------|---------|
| `app-page-header` | `shared/components/data/page-header` | Title + count badge + action slot |
| `app-data-table` | `shared/components/data/data-table` | Generic table with sort, skeleton, groupSeparator, actions |
| `app-filter-bar` | `shared/components/data/filter-bar` | `<ng-content>` wrapper + "Netejar filtres" |
| `app-active-filters` | `shared/components/data/active-filters` | Dismissible badge chips |
| `app-column-toggle` | `shared/components/data/column-toggle` | Collapse with checkbox per column |
| `app-pagination` | `shared/components/data/pagination` | Join buttons + per-page selector |
| `app-empty-state` | `shared/components/data/empty-state` | Icon + message + optional CTA |
| `app-stat-card` | `shared/components/data/stat-card` | DaisyUI stat |
| `app-form-field` | `shared/components/forms/form-field` | Label + error + helper wrapper |
| `app-confirm-dialog` | `shared/components/feedback/confirm-dialog` | Native `<dialog>` modal |
| `app-toast` + `ToastService` | `shared/components/feedback/toast` | Auto-dismiss alerts |

## Data Table Contract

Pass ALL columns with `value` extractors. Let `app-data-table` handle visibility:

```html
<app-data-table
  [items]="items()"
  [columns]="tableColumns()"
  [visibleColumns]="visibleColumnKeys()"
  [sortBy]="sortBy()"
  [sortOrder]="sortOrder()"
  [loading]="loading()"
  [rowActions]="rowActions"
  (rowClick)="onRowClick($any($event).id)"
  (sortChange)="onSortChange($event)"
/>
```

Sort cycle: ASC â†’ DESC â†’ clear (3-state).

## Visual Hierarchy

- Page title: `text-xl font-bold` + `badge badge-neutral badge-lg` for count
- Cards: `card bg-base-100 shadow-sm`. Accent borders: `border-l-4 border-primary`
- Labels: `text-xs text-base-content/50 font-medium`
- Values: `text-sm text-base-content`
- Muted: `text-base-content/60`. Very muted: `text-base-content/40`

## Loading & Empty States

- Tables: inline skeleton rows inside `app-data-table` (automatic via `[loading]`)
- Pages: `loading loading-spinner loading-md text-primary`
- Empty: always use `app-empty-state` with Lucide icon + Catalan message + CTA
- Cards: use `app-skeleton-cards` with static grid class map (no dynamic Tailwind)

## Accessibility

- All interactive elements keyboard-navigable
- Buttons include text or `aria-label`
- `type="button"` on all non-submit buttons
- Dropdowns: DaisyUI `dropdown` + `tabindex="0"` pattern
